	I hope you all are happy with each and every of your HANDYBOARDS, because
I am not.

	I have just solved my RESET problem by changing the "tri-state bus
controller" 74hc244 chip, I can RESET my HB by switching it off first, then
on. This could be useful for those having the same problem as mine. And a
special thanks to Maz Rahm for his contribution.

	After the above problem solved, I decided to change the switches of the HB
to the ones I bought from electronic stores. The start and stop switch were
replaced by a normally-open switch, but alot bigger compared to the one
originally used.

